Params: {1: '1', 2: 'Liv', 3: "We've returned to somewhere near the ruins when we first engaged with the Corrupted. Now we'll just have to follow Kamui's signal through the excavated paths.", 4: '3'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lee', 3: 'Looks like the Corrupted that attacked us left already.', 4: '3'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: 'How can you leave Nanami out of this! Nanami helped you out sooo much last time!', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: "You ungrateful, heartless people! What color is your blood?! Nanami's so hurt she's gonna cry now! Any second!", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Liv', 3: "Bianca's completely unbothered by Nanami, she really knows how to handle her...", 4: '3'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Bianca', 3: 'Just keep calm and walk at your own pace.', 4: '3'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: "Oh wow, withering obasans and the blossoming youth don't mix! Nanami can't handle it, her vitality is dying!", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Liv', 3: "Nanami too... She's keeping her own pace as well.", 4: '3'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Bianca', 3: 'No, not really. She appeared out of nowhere on a mission of ours and disrupted us a few times.', 4: '3'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: "Hm? Hmm? Hmmmm? Wait, what did Nanami hear? Nanami's floating around in ecstasy—No, don't stop me!", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: 'Y-you are all worrying about Nanami! And even said you would give Nanami a good time by letting her join in your mission!', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: "Nanami is so touched she's fully revived now! Nanami will definitely help you!", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: "Let's go let's go! Time's ticking! If you need to find a missing person, Nanami's your detective—", 4: '1'}
